//customer -> 公共样式  tips：每个公共样式写明实现的是什么功能以方便查阅
//更改时间选择插件的’至‘范围
@import "./variable.styl"

.el-date-editor .el-range-separator
  width: 10%

.el-date-editor .el-range__close-icon
  display: none

//  鼠标移入时变手
.hand
  cursor: pointer

//input的交互效果
input.input-height-item:hover, .input-height-item:hover
  border: 1px solid #999 !important

.input-height
  border: 2px solid rgba(102, 102, 102, .2) !important
  border-radius: 5px
  input.input-height-item, .input-height-item
    border: 1px solid #999 !important

//订单查询的时间插件样式
.order-block
  .el-date-editor--daterange.el-input, .el-date-editor--daterange.el-input__inner, .el-date-editor--timerange.el-input, .el-date-editor--timerange.el-input__inner
    width: 17vw
    margin-left: 10px
    height: 30px
    padding: 3px 16px 3px 10px
  .el-date-editor .el-range__icon
    transform: translateY(-20%)
  .el-date-editor .el-range-input
    transform: translateY(-20%)
    width: 38%
  .el-date-editor .el-range-separator
    transform: translateY(-20%)
    width: 11%
  .el-date-editor .el-range__close-icon
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    right: -2px
    display: block

.open
  .el-date-editor
    width: 17vw
    .el-input__suffix
      right: 18%
  .el-date-editor .el-range-input
    font-size: 13px

.end-time
  .order-block
    width: 65%
    height: 75%
    .el-date-editor.el-input, .el-date-editor.el-input__inner
      z-index: 0
      height: 90%
      width: 100%
    .el-input__inner
      width: 100%
      height: 100%
      padding: 0
      padding-left: 8px
      border: none
    .el-input__icon
      display: none
    .el-input__prefix
      display: none
  &:hover
    .el-input__inner
      background: #F5F7FB

.end-time
  .order-boder
    .el-input__inner
      border: 0.5px solid #ccc
      &:hover
        border: 1px solid #999 !important
    &:hover
      .el-input__inner
        background: #ffffff
.tap-first
  .block
    .el-date-editor--datetimerange.el-input, .el-date-editor--datetimerange.el-input__inner
      line-height: 30px
      width: 100%
      height: 100%
      padding-top: 0
      padding-bottom: 0
      overflow :hidden



